C     NAME      MEANING                                  DEFAULT VALUE  
C     ------------------------------------------------------------------
C     MXDBHT    MAXIMUM LENGTH OF WORK AREA IN /DOUBLE/        450      
C               FOR DOUBLE HETEROGENEOUS CELL CALCULATION               
